        Joan issued a scathing reply, saying: "Trash talk for the sake of denigrating women doing their jobs is at best misogynistic and at worst undignified and ignorant!"Grande then clapped back at Morgan with a series of tweets of her own about women's right to choose to show their bodies off.
    
      
              
