        He then asked if her screensaver was him posing naked, before asking her to come on his Good Morning Britain show to "settle things".While that's unlikely to happen, Morgan seemed very pleased with the outcome of the row. As he probably intended, his name was trending worldwide on Twitter after her tweets.
    
      
              
